virtual FDO_API void FdoINetworkCommand::SetExcludeNodes (  GisString *  className,
FdoFilter *  filter
)  [pure virtual]
 

This method is used to set an optional filter that resolve to a set of nodes that need to be excluded.

Parameters:
className is the class name used to set the context of the filter.
filter a filter that defines a group of nodes.
Returns:
Returns nothing
